    <h2 class="section-left">Background</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="col-sm-6">
  <p>While there are many great tools that ease the friction that comes with communicating with a remote team, there arenâ€™t many that help you to collaborate. Video conferencing tools like Hangouts, Zoom, etc., allow you share control of your mouse with attendeesâ€”but the constant back and forth of control inhibits the work getting done.</p>

  <p>The value proposition of Podium was to give remote team the ability to get things tasks done in the apps they already use.</p>
  </div>
</div>

